snippet.title: Metal: Hellsinger VR – Demo Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Metal: Hellsinger, the pure metal rhythm shooter with the multi award-winning soundtrack is coming to VR and releasing Fall 2024! Play the new demo on Steam now.

Play the Demo: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2878270/Metal_Hellsinger_VR/

#metalhellsinger #steamvr #vr 

Follow us on our official social media channels to never miss a beat:

Twitter: https://twitter.com/metalhellsinger
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/MetalHellsinger/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/metalhellsinger/
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@metalhellsinger
